SEARCH
Package au.csiro.pathling.search

Class SearchParameterRegistry

java.lang.Object
au.csiro.pathling.search.SearchParameterRegistry
public class SearchParameterRegistry extends Object
Registry for FHIR search parameter definitions.

This is a pure data holder that maps resource types to their available search parameters. Use the static factory methods to create instances.
